{"tid":1984432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你仲記得6月9日個種團結嗎？","createTime":"2020-04-22T12:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T12:59:28.000Z","uid":294153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24595821b2f15a10327170731843698e9e8e8a0d","tid":1984432,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2019年6月9日    百萬人遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n運動將近一年，我會每日同大家回帶每一個重要日期<br />\n因為6月9號係我正式投入運動嘅開始，所以我會由6月9號記錄起</span><br />\n<br />\n百萬人大遊行顯示咗香港人對抗極權嘅決心<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSifg9N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSifg9N.png&h=22e01042&s={SIZE}\" />令政治冷感嘅香港人團結一齊<br />\n<br />\n用和理非嘅手段要求政府撤回惡法<br />\n結果遊行未完，正苦就宣布會如期（6月12）進行二讀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/21/020350_68c8c733b36e8d94f7a6380040191050.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F21%2F020350_68c8c733b36e8d94f7a6380040191050.jpeg&h=37bfa53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是政府教會我哋和平示威冇用<br />\n更令我哋知道呢個政府係唔會聆聽民意<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，堅持到底。<br />\n毋忘721 831 101 中大 理大<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">莫忘初衷</span></span></strong><br />\n街上見。"},{"pid":"2f2533556d30de73824bf676cc917a22eaa2d77c","tid":1984432,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d588bf26a8402820654c6a1872650204ace01167","tid":1984432,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"歡迎留名share大家最深刻嘅日期"},{"pid":"e1e86e65be962dd77382da596d0527cf16d1be66","tid":1984432,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:57:05.000Z","msg":"回望翻6月嘅連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dca1263d8765c511d9eab55e18caf3349f87231","tid":1984432,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"唔好再鬥黃"},{"pid":"e52b91c86cbd32a50492905df6cd889ec9ca69e4","tid":1984432,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"一日未光復到香港 我一日都會企出嚟"},{"pid":"e3181c278e901ef1bd2c90d15bd22a7f94f67050","tid":1984432,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:59:28.000Z","msg":"記得仲有 Twitter戰線要打"}]}